QuestData.Title: Help Mama Wheeler
QuestData.Description: Say, $n, I was wondering if you could do me another favor.$B$BMy partner out in the field could probably use a hand. I was wondering if you could go check in on her.$B$BI'm sure that Mama Wheeler will appreciate the help. Just don't mind her sharp tongue.$B$BShe's trying to look out for our interests to the east. You'll find her just inside Eco-Dome Midrealm at the Midrealm Post.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Mama Wheeler at the Midrealm Post inside Eco-Dome Midrealm in the Netherstorm.
QuestData.RewardText: What?! He called me his 'partner'? I'm his wife!$B$BAnd he said I had a sharp tongue! Ooh, when I get back to Area 52, I'm going to box his big, green ears!$B$BBut I'm glad that you're here. He was right about one thing; I can definitely use your help!
